== Class Change System ==

=== Requirements ===

{| class="wikitable"
! Requirement !! Details
|-
| Level || Must be level 20+
|-
| Location || Dharma Temple
|-
| Hero || Cannot change class
|}

=== Effects ===

When changing class:
* Level resets to 1
* Stats halved
* Keeps learned spells
* Learns new class spells

=== Optimal Paths ===

{| class="wikitable"
! Starting Class !! Recommended Change !! Reason
|-
